   Hardware Specification for Combined Econet and User Port Expansion Card
  =========================================================================

  The Econet interface shall be functionally identical to the current
Econet daughter board, it will have collision detect.  It will operate
correctly with the following computers and equipment, BBC Micro Computer,
the Master, the FileStore (both original and stacking), the Acorn Econet
Bridge, the PC-EcoLink card, the SJ Bridge, the SJ FDFS and MDFS, and all
Archimedes computers.  It will be capable of operating at a clock speed of
200KHz.

  As a podule it will have a manufacturer code of 0 (for Acorn) and a
product type identifier of 7.

